明智之举 - 无论它是您的日常驾驶者还是仅使用它来执行一些选定的任务。 <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfAP4frCSWpQqpijLBMO6_wEwwDt_g_nEekuQIjSBa6J&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAnker-PowerCore-Portable-Double-Speed-Recharging%2Fdp%2FB01JIWQPMW">Anker 的 PowerCore 26,800</a>具有足够高的容量，可为大多数平板电脑充电几乎两倍，因此您在到达下一个目的地之前不太可能完全耗尽电量。虽然它不能为笔记本电脑充电，但它适用于大多数移动设备，并且它具有三个 USB-A 端口，因此您可以同时为最多三个设备供电。由于砖块本身的重量仅超过一磅，因此它也不会整天给您的包带来压力。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-ipad-accessories-130018595.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-ipad-accessories-130018595.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 94f7e0a4-2c37-37fd-9879-739177ccbf4c</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jul 2023 14:30:18 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688481019</ingested><modified> 2023-07-04T14:30:35+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[anker]]></category><category><![CDATA[otterbox]]></category><category><![CDATA[SanDisk]]></category><category><![CDATA[screenprotector]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[ixpand]]></category><category><![CDATA[HyperDrive]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[magickeyboard]]></category><category><![CDATA[RAVPower]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPadPro]]></category><category><![CDATA[Logitech]]></category><category><![CDATA[ipad]]></category><category><![CDATA[usb-c]]></category><category><![CDATA[ApplePencil]]></category><category><![CDATA[powerbank]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category