pecific bags can get pricey.</p><h2>三星 Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="82b39bb57d2e41dab1c787229046a5f2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjVUQjNRP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE0YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzkxN2MyMmEtNzg4OS00YzMyLWEyZDktOTVhYWNkYTFkMjExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAWiQntQfuL-DpTNEDx9m5QPh_cN-L6WPbhTNq0SxIGRo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J5TB3Q">Samsung Galaxy Watch 5</a> is down to $199 for a 40mm model and $229 for a <a data-i13n="cpos:63;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIySjRXNVRUP3RoPTEmdGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU1TmQmGcWLZhjXtQLGpqR2ggaG5X4r_eZuqNKt3fF-7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B2J4W5TT%3Fth%3D1">44mm model</a> . We gave the Galaxy Watch 5 a <a data-i13n="cpos:64;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-5-pro-review-battery-life-specs-durability-180052187.html">score of 85</a> last year, and it&#39;s currently the &quot;best for Android users&quot; pick in our <a data-i13n="cpos:65;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">smartwatch buying guide</a> . While its battery life could be better, its design is durable and attractive, its OS is easy to navigate and its health tracking is relatively comprehensive. Samsung is expected to announce a <a data-i13n="cpos:66;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-6-leak-suggests-the-rotating-bezel-will-return-124637657.html">Galaxy Watch 6</a> in the coming weeks, however, so it may be worth waiting to see how that model stacks up if you don&#39;t need a new smartwatch right this instant.</p><h2> Google Pixel 7a + Pixel Buds A-Series </h2><p><core-commerce id="bc03f3966efb4f8381f72684ce1d5060" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Amazon knocked $100 off a bundle that includes the <a data-i13n="cpos:67;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUEmoHTd7IM41V8YPjc4ugbl9KKmEQ5JFRVAtyp_zVOe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGoogle-Pixel-7a-128GB-Charcoal-Pixel%2Fdp%2FB0C7WB7FGS">Google Pixel 7a smartphone and the Pixel Buds A-Series</a> , bringing it down to $499. This is a great bundle if you&#39;ve needed a phone upgrade but didn&#39;t want to spend a ton of money. The Pixel 7a is the <a data-i13n="cpos:68;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-engadget-guide-to-the-best-midrange-smartphones-120050366.html">best midrange phone</a> you can get right now, thanks to its fast Tensor G2 chipset, smooth 90Hz display, IP67 water resistance, fantastic cameras and support for wireless charging. The <a data-i13n="cpos:69;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-buds-a-series-review-160054961.html">Pixel Buds A-Series</a> are almost the earbud-complement to the Pixel 7a — they&#39;re not as feature-rich as the Pixel Buds Pro, but they have deep Google Assistant integration, solid sound quality and a comfy fit.</p><h2> Xbox Wireless Headset </h2><p><core-commerce id="25e00f2e1fe74058a0ce3adda98c2fc8" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQM7M4HYS1IhDJ9sJLFr5FCPsx7iHzGrOJ97tAjATg9O&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FXbox-Wireless-Headset-One-Windows-Devices%2Fdp%2FB08WFD42G5%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Xbox&#39;s Wireless Headset</a> is 20 percent off and down to $80 right now. It&#39;s designed to work with the Xbox Series X, S and One, along with Windows 10 devices, too. It supports spatial audio technologies including Windows Sonic, Dolby Atmos, and DTS Headphone:X, and it has up to 15 hours of battery life.</p><p> <strong><em>Your Prime Day Shopping Guide:</em></strong> <em>See all of our</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day</em></a> <em>coverage.</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳科技优惠</em></a><em>。 Learn about</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://www.intheknow.com/tag/prime-day/"><em>Prime Day trends</em></a> <em>on In the Know, and hear from Autoblog&#39;s car experts on must-shop auto-related</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:75;pos:1" href="https://www.autoblog.com/tag/prime+day/"><em>Prime Day deals</em></a> <em>.</em></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/2023-amazon-prime-day-early-access-deals-124853564.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/2023-amazon-prime-day-early-access-deals-124853564.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7917c22a-7889-4c32-a2d9-95aacda1d211</guid><dc:creator> Jeff Dunn,Amy Skorheim</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jul 2023 12:48:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688474937</ingested><modified> 2023-07-04T12:49:14+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="534" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/59cf8c60-0b99-11ee-bfdd-c5b04492c845" width="800"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/e5ce4ba0-0ad8-11ee-affe-11bc09e9224c" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Amazon Prime Day]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Amazon Prime Day]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple wants to take the Epic Games case to the Supreme Court]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/legal/apple-ask-us-supreme-court-undo-app-store-order-epic-games-case-2023-07-03/"><em>据路透社</em>报道</a>，苹果正在采取最后的努力来维持应用内销售的削减，要求最高法院听取其对 Epic Games 反垄断案件的上诉。两个下级法院裁定，苹果必须放弃阻止应用程序包含自己的支付选项的指导方针，这一政策有助于苹果的盈利。</p><p>这场战斗始于 2020 年，当时 Epic 推出了新的<em>《堡垒之夜》</em>更新，允许玩家通过直接支付功能购买数字硬币。此举违反了苹果公司要求所有 iOS 游戏都使用应用内购买的政策，并让苹果公司抽取了 30% 的利润。作为回应， <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-fortnite-ios-app-store-court-appeals-epic-games-175240669.html">苹果公司将<em>《堡垒之夜》</em>从其应用商店中删除</a>，尽管它一直是其收入最高的游戏之一。作为报复， <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fortnite-maker-epic-games-sues-apple-195415590.html">Epic 起诉苹果公司</a>终止其“不公平和反竞争行为”，目的是改变其政策而不是寻求任何损害赔偿。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这起诉讼对双方来说都是一个复杂的问题：2021 年，美国地区法官伊冯·冈萨雷斯·罗杰斯 (Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers) 裁定 Epic 故意违反了苹果的规定，并且 iPhone 制造商无需将<em>《堡垒之夜》</em>重新添加到其应用商店中。罗杰斯还表示，苹果的行为并不像垄断者，但该公司必须允许应用程序向用户提供第三方支付系统。这一变化于去年生效， <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-wins-appeals-court-ruling-against-epic-games-191331514.html">美国第九巡回上诉法院于今年四月维持了整个禁令</a>。</p><p>苹果律师在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://fingfx.thomsonreuters.com/gfx/legaldocs/egpbyzkmjvq/Apple%20Supreme%20Court%20petition%202023-07-03.pdf">文件</a>中声称，该裁决超出了 Epic Games 的范围，并且“超出了地区法院根据第三条的权限，该条款将联邦法院的管辖权限制在实际案件和争议上。”基本上，他们认为法院做得太过分了，并要求最高法院承认这一点，并让其应用商店恢复正常运营（开发商向苹果提供但减少销售）。无论如何，苹果至少必须适应一些国家的情况， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-12-13/will-apple-allow-users-to-install-third-party-app-stores-sideload-in-europe">欧盟新法规</a>要求该公司在 2024 年之前允许第三方应用商店。</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/apple-wants-to-take-the-epic-games-case-to-the-supreme-court-123501115.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-wants-to-take-the-epic-games-case-to-the-supreme-court-123501115.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7dfae2ea-aea1-46e6-96b5-ea18d492aab3</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc: