etflix</a></ins> 。伊萨·雷 (Issa Rae) 广受好评的喜剧剧集<em>《不安全》</em>的全部五季现已在美国 Netflix 上播出。更多 HBO 剧集也即将上线。该公司表示，作为交易的一部分<em>，《兄弟连》、《太平洋》、《六尺之下》</em>和<em>《Ballers》</em>也将登陆 Netflix<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://deadline.com/2023/07/hbos-insecure-launches-on-netflix-six-feet-under-others-coming-next-1235429245/"><em>最后期限</em></a></ins>。与此同时，美国以外的 Netflix 用户可以在该服务上观看<em>《真爱如血》</em> 。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hbo-shows-are-streaming-on-netflix-in-the-us-for-the-first-time-161235695.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-metas-instagram-linked-twitter-rival-could-arrive-this-week-111508536.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-metas-instagram-linked-twitter-rival-could-arrive-this-week-111508536.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 39112938-c0de-44e9-ba1a-fb9250c8a141</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jul 2023 11:15:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688464815</ingested><modified> 2023-07-04T10:00:20+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="1000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/06c338b0-1a2a-11ee-8ebf-014a6eda512e" width="1600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:i